    {
      "id": "6d0d5779-0b68-4b3b-8796-eb107c0e91e5",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $P \\in {\\C[X]}$ de racines $x_1,x_2,\\dots,x_n$ avec les multiplicit{\\'e}s\n$m_1,m_2,\\dots,m_n$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P \\in {\\C[X]}\\)</span> de racines <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_1,x_2,\\dots,x_n\\)</span> avec les multiplicit<span>é</span>s <span class=\"math inline\">\\(m_1,m_2,\\dots,m_n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5ecc3804-ff36-49b3-b347-5f79cfeb0a55",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}composer en {\\'e}l{\\'e}ments simples $\\frac {P'}P$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>composer en <span>é</span>l<span>é</span>ments simples <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac {P&#39;}P\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7893d9f2-1152-438c-ae34-f81548a01df7",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$P' = \\sum_{i=1}^n \\frac {m_iP}{X-x_i}  \\Rightarrow \n             \\frac {P'}P = \\sum_{i=1}^n \\frac {m_i}{X-x_i}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(P&#39; = \\sum_{i=1}^n \\frac {m_iP}{X-x_i}  \\Rightarrow \n             \\frac {P&#39;}P = \\sum_{i=1}^n \\frac {m_i}{X-x_i}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ce174706-9374-450c-968a-16eda5831551",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire que les racines de $P'$ sont dans l'enveloppe convexe\n    de $x_1,\\dots,x_n$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire que les racines de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P&#39;\\)</span> sont dans l’enveloppe convexe de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_1,\\dots,x_n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5a582de9-d6c4-470b-bac5-5d080ebec5b4",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$P'(z) = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\sum_{i=1}^n m_i\\frac {\\overline{z-x_i}}{|z-x_i|^2} = 0\n             \\Leftrightarrow z = \\text{Bar}\\biggl( x_i, \\frac {m_i}{|z-x_i|^2} \\biggr)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(P&#39;(z) = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\sum_{i=1}^n m_i\\frac {\\overline{z-x_i}}{|z-x_i|^2} = 0\n             \\Leftrightarrow z = \\text{Bar}\\biggl( x_i, \\frac {m_i}{|z-x_i|^2} \\biggr)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
